{"tid":2510634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印度破1800萬確診！25年挖墳工不穿防護衣：怕也沒用","createTime":"2021-04-30T09:47:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T11:18:55.000Z","uid":50740,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1e0f82bd73b82b1a159f0352f3ca9719288fb6f7","tid":2510634,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:47:43.000Z","msg":"印度新冠肺炎（COVID-19）疫情大爆發，孟買的從事挖墳工作的工人必須24小時輪班，來應付激增的死亡病患。但是在當地的掘墓工，卻沒有穿防護衣，更有已經入行25年的老員工坦言「怕也沒用」，自己是靠著勇氣努力工做下去。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/30/3133498-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F30%2F3133498-PH.jpg&h=0084d976&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印度的疫情嚴峻，過去一週至少每天增加30萬例確診，29日累計染疫人數已突破1800萬。印度的醫療體系和火葬場，都已負荷過重，甚至到處都有臨時火葬場在焚化成堆的遺體。<br />\n<br />\n根據《路透社》報導，52歲的坎姆魯丁在在孟買已掘墓25年，他和同事現在日以繼夜埋葬染疫亡者，不斷重複著「接收遺體，把遺體移出救護車，然後埋葬」的動作，至今已1年沒有休假。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmToYmyjwZbUZP6FXr4CNsc5ib4rEBs7GW728BgNoVr43j?filename=iPiwUqu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiPiwUqu.jpg&h=4008e747&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n他更透露，從去年疫情爆發後約2至3個月後，他就不再穿防護衣物，直接上工，並坦言，要做這項工作，必須要有膽量勇氣，怕也沒有用，信仰讓他能夠堅持下去。"},{"pid":"83d495105cafd0de7acfd1e8f939c6b8cc50fd6d","tid":2510634,"uid":219085,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:49:38.000Z","msg":"印度熱狗<br />\n不做恐懼撚"},{"pid":"264441bfb1d35c1676d107171df027ee857d212c","tid":2510634,"uid":135787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:52:41.000Z","msg":"如果信仰有用就唔會有咁多墳要掘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢咁搞法衰d講遲早真係幫自己掘埋墳<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/coffin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b92a1c47e84fa906ca166f7d329ba58b78e34fa7","tid":2510634,"uid":99962,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:53:51.000Z","msg":"其實好慘，笑唔出"},{"pid":"1bbc5af9b569926bb057f964c6ec63cf2f692b9c","tid":2510634,"uid":57513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"83d495105cafd0de7acfd1e8f939c6b8cc50fd6d","tid":2510634,"uid":219085,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:49:38.000Z","msg":"印度熱狗<br />\n不做恐懼撚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:02:04.000Z","msg":"無人係印度post講輕感冒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7dfef1e718c49a1cd0ea4868e13249b874eeef4","tid":2510634,"uid":75445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:47:07.000Z","msg":"係窮呀⋯"},{"pid":"248c3374ca252fc9ed9a2d8712b6302a4cd7b4c6","tid":2510634,"uid":152705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bbc5af9b569926bb057f964c6ec63cf2f692b9c","tid":2510634,"uid":57513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"83d495105cafd0de7acfd1e8f939c6b8cc50fd6d","tid":2510634,"uid":219085,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:49:38.000Z","msg":"印度熱狗<br />\n不做恐懼撚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:02:04.000Z","msg":"無人係印度post講輕感冒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:10:39.000Z","msg":"召喚無懼撚P牌仔&ldquo;你問&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"089567046a7c1d52ee5ecfe7c7e79fd00d315c2f","tid":2510634,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:18:55.000Z","msg":"你埋落去嗰啲咪講完怕也沒用囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/cigar.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}